Package: kentr
Type: Package
Title: Sequence data analysis tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Kent", "Riemondy", email = "kent.riemondy@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for processing sequencing data in R. Incorporates the htslib 
             C library for accessing bam and fasta files via Rcpp functions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
    Rcpp,
    dplyr (>= 0.5.0),
    purrr,
    readr,
    stringr,
    R.utils
SystemRequirements: C++11 GNU make
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.8)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
URL: http://github.com/kriemo/kentr, http://kriemo.github.io/kentr
BugReports: https://github.com/kriemo/kentr/issues
